<font class="content"><P align=center><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Letmebegin.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR><STRONG>I would have to say Tiane put that right o­n the mark. The Alliance marched into the Plane of Time with many goals in mind, those goals and more were accomplished.<BR><BR>But First - To get to the Plane of Time you have to kill these four annoying bastards, and then backflag them, and backflag them and backflag them...........<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/TimeAccess.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR>Ok, so you've killed these all about five or six times right? Good, now you get to phase1, 2, and 3....boring...kill mobs...get loot. Then there is the later phases, in phase4 you get to see some old buddies.<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Phase4.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR>Yep! The zek brothers are dead <BR>Whats that three times you have to kill them in order to progress? You'd think they would learn to just get the hell out of the way. So, ok...phase5?! Wow the Alliance made it that far already? More old friends!~<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Phase5.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR>(Oh ya, Bertox is in there somewhere, but well he died first attempt, dropped loot, body in the wall!)<BR><BR>The Plane of Time, it's fun...and rewarding. It's like the developers just decided to say, well...if they keep playing this long lets just throw more and more loot at them, by the time you make it to phase5, the loot begins to look something like this there is just so much of it..<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/CombinedLoot.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR><BR>Well -- Thats it, total kills for the Alliance o­n Friday February 20 and Saturday the 21st<BR>Phase o­ne Cleared: Loots x10<BR>Phase Two Cleared: Loots x 5<BR>Phase Three Cleared: Loots x3 (Wow yah we got lucky there)<BR>Phase Four Cleared: Loots x12<BR>Phase Five: Cazic Thule, Bertox, Rallos 25%: Loots - again, something like 6 pieces. <BR>Grats to all the winners.<BR><BR>And - don't say we don't ever update the page!</STRONG></P><BR><BR>
</font>
